title: Ultimate Survival Alaska Season 1 720p
description:
Eight survivalist men are dropped off by plane in the Alaskan wilderness where they compete in a 3,000-mile race through Alaska's unpredictable weather, barren landscapes, and hostile predators. Each episode in the series documents the survivalists' experiences at a specific location point of their 3,000-mile race. The main goal for the survivalists in each episode is to survive with very little gear they have and to reach a certain destination point in 72 hours.
